trans-unit.source: Contains a cache of XML Schema definition language (XSD) and XML-Data Reduced (XDR) schemas.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en hurtigbuffer for datadefinisjonsspråk for XML-skjema (XSD) og XML-Data redusert (XDR)-skjemaer.

trans-unit.source: The XmlSchemaCollection class class is obsolete.
Schemas are loaded using the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaCollection.Add%2A> method, at which time the schema is associated with a namespace Uniform Resource Identifier (URI).
trans-unit.target: XML-skjemaer er lastet inn med den <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaCollection.Add%2A>metoden, da skjemaet er knyttet til et navneområde Uniform URI (Resource Identifier).</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: For XML Schemas, this will typically be the `targetNamespace` property of the schema.
trans-unit.target: For XML-skjema dette vanligvis blir den `targetNamespace` for skjemaet.

trans-unit.source: Although this class stores both XML Schemas and XDR schemas, any method and property that takes or returns an <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> applies to XML Schemas only.
trans-unit.target: Selv om denne klassen lagrer både XML-skjemaer og XDR-skjemaer, noen metoder og egenskaper som tar eller returnerer en <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>gjelder bare for XML-skjemaer.</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>

trans-unit.source: This version of the product supports the World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) XML Schema recommendation located at http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema-1 and http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema-2.
trans-unit.target: Denne versjonen av produktet støtter World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) XML-skjema anbefaler på http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema-1 og http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema-2.

trans-unit.source: An XML Schema must reference the W3C Schema namespace `http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema` in its schema element.
trans-unit.target: Et XML-skjema må referere til navneområdet W3C skjemaet `http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema` i schema-elementet.

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaCollection.Add%2A> method for an example.
`XmlSchemaCollection` can be used by <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> for efficient data validation.
> [!IMPORTANT] > The XmlSchemaCollection class is obsolete in the Microsoft .NET Framework version 2.0 and has been replaced by the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet> class.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > For XmlSchemaCollection klassen er foreldet i Microsoft .NET Framework, versjon 2.0 og har blitt erstattet med <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet>klasse.</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaCollection" name="XmlSchemaCollection" href=""></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaCollection" name="XmlSchemaCollection" href=""> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > The <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaCollection> class is obsolete in the .NET Framework version 2.0 and has been replaced by the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet> class.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT]> For <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaCollection>klassen er foreldet i .NET Framework-versjon 2.0 og har blitt erstattet med <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet>klasse.</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet> </xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaCollection>
